## 3 — Structural Debt

### 3.1 Redundant / Near-Duplicate Components

| Group | Components | Issue |
|-------|-----------|-------|
| **Map panels** | [AQIMaps](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/AQIMaps.tsx#4-165), [EmissionMaps](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/EmissionMaps.tsx#4-189), [SectorMaps](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/SectorMaps.tsx#13-213) | All 3 follow the **identical pattern**: two side-by-side `glass-panel` cards with `<img>` tags, year `<select>`, refresh `<button>`, "Interactive View" link, `onError`/`onLoad` handlers. ~500 combined lines that could be a single `<MapPanel>` component. |
| **Chart wrappers** | [EmissionForecast](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/EmissionForecast.tsx#28-211), [AQITrends](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/AQITrends.tsx#23-179), [HistoricEmissions](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/HistoricEmissions.tsx#28-242) | All 3 share: glass-panel with loading overlay spinner, recharts `<LineChart>` inside `<ResponsiveContainer>`, identical Tooltip styling, identical axis styling, identical CartesianGrid config. ~630 combined lines with ≈80% structural overlap. |
| **Chat interfaces** | [HealthChat](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/HealthChat.tsx#14-145) (in LiveAQI flow), PolicySimulator inline chat | Both are chat UIs with identical message bubble patterns, typing indicators (bouncing dots), input+send layout. Separately implemented. |
| **AQI data interfaces** | [AQIData](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/LiveAQI.tsx#6-18) interface in [LiveAQI.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/LiveAQI.tsx), [AQIData](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/LiveAQI.tsx#6-18) interface in [GlobalStateContext.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/context/GlobalStateContext.tsx) | ⛔ **Duplicate interface declaration.** Same fields, defined twice. |
| **Impact interfaces** | [Impact](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/CausalGraph.tsx#35-57) in [CausalGraph.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/CausalGraph.tsx), [Impact](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/CausalGraph.tsx#35-57) (identical) in [ImpactPanel.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/ImpactPanel.tsx) | ⛔ **Duplicate interface declaration.** Should be shared type. |
| **Unused code** | `ProgressBar` in [ImpactPanel.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/ImpactPanel.tsx) (lines 192-234) | Entire component is commented out, taking up 40 lines. Dead code. |
| **Unused imports** | [AQIHealthImpact.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/AQIHealthImpact.tsx) line 21: `// ... imports stay same ...` | Dead comment left from refactoring. |

### 3.2 Naming Inconsistencies

| Issue | Examples |
|-------|---------|
| **Export style** | [Navigation](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/Navigation.tsx#7-66) = default export, [LiveAQI](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/LiveAQI.tsx#19-102) = named export `{ LiveAQI }`, [AQIHealthImpact](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/AQIHealthImpact.tsx#119-312) = default export, [PolicySimulator](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/PolicySimulator.tsx#106-1177) = named export `{ PolicySimulator }`, [Reveal](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/Reveal.tsx#11-48) = named export. **No consistent pattern.** |
| **File ↔ export name** | [HealthChat.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/HealthChat.tsx) exports `{ HealthChat }` (named), [HealthImpact.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/HealthImpact.tsx) exports `{ HealthImpact }` (named), [CausalGraph.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/CausalGraph.tsx) exports `default CausalGraph`. Inconsistent. |
| **Prop typing** | [HealthImpact](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/HealthImpact.tsx#10-171) takes `aqiData: any` ⛔. [HealthChat](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/HealthChat.tsx#14-145) takes `aqiContext: any` ⛔. Strong types exist in [GlobalStateContext.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/context/GlobalStateContext.tsx) but are not referenced. |
| **Variable naming** | `aiqChange` (typo in [ImpactPanel.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/CURRENT/DigitalTwin/digital-twin-frontend/src/components/ImpactPanel.tsx) line 45 — should be `aqiChange`). |

